DESC:"Collection milestones for defeating sketches in each rarity. Each rarity awards medals at 25%, 50%, 75%, and full Glossary completion.",MEDAL_CAT_TOOLS_DESC:"Medals for building out the Shop toolkit and putting those tools to work, from unlocking more options to using specialized tools often.",MEDAL_CAT_FENG_SHUI_DESC:"Arrangement medals for displaying specific groups of sketches together in the Gallery. Hide unrelated sketches to isolate the group; maxed sketches can be unhidden and still count.",MEDAL_CAT_SPECS_DESC:"Medals for reaching notable battle spec values. Most follow normal progression, while later targets may need a focused setup or strategy.",MEDAL_CAT_TRUE_FEATS_DESC:"Unusual achievements that reward experimentation and out-of-the-box thinking. Some clues are cryptic, but the Medal X-Ray tool can eventually reveal exactly how to earn each one.",SHOP_MARKET_HEADER:"Tools",SHOP_FILTER_ALL:"All",SHOP_HIDE_PURCHASED:"Hide Purchased",SHOP_UNLOCK_BUTTON:"Unlock",SHOP_UNLOCKED_LABEL:"UNLOCKED",SHOP_PROTOCOLS_HEADER:"Active Protocols",SHOP_PROTOCOL_ACTIVATION_HINT:"Must activate in the Protocols panel",PROTOCOL_ACTIVE:"Active",PROTOCOL_DISABLED:"Disabled",SHOP_AUDIT_THRESHOLD:"Audit Threshold",SHOP_NO_PROTOCOLS:"No active protocols available",SHOP_UNLOCK_HINT:"Unlock special tools.",SHOP_TOGGLE_AUTO_BUY_ALL:"Toggle All Auto",SHOP_AFFORDABLE_ONLY:"Affordable Only",SHOP_TAB_TOOLS:"Tools",SHOP_TAB_UPGRADES:"Stat Upgrades",SHOP_TAB_MEDALS:"Feat Medals",UPGRADE_HP_GRAPHITE_NAME:"Thick Paper",UPGRADE_HP_GRAPHITE_DESC:"+6% HP per level",UPGRADE_ATK_GRAPHITE_NAME:"Bold Lines",UPGRADE_ATK_GRAPHITE_DESC:"+5% ATK per level",UPGRADE_SPD_GRAPHITE_NAME:"Quick Strokes",UPGRADE_SPD_GRAPHITE_DESC:"+1% SPD per level",UPGRADE_CRITDMG_WAX_NAME:"Sharp Edges",UPGRADE_CRITDMG_WAX_DESC:"+1% Crit DMG per level",UPGRADE_ATK_WAX_NAME:"Wax Seal",UPGRADE_ATK_WAX_DESC:"+8% ATK per level",UPGRADE_DODGE_WAX_NAME:"Liquid Motion",UPGRADE_DODGE_WAX_DESC:"+0.5% Dodge per level",UPGRADE_HP_