ND_MULTISTRIKECHANCEINCREASE_DESC:"Bonus Multi Strike Chance percentage.",FUND_FREEZECHANCEINCREASE_LABEL:"Freeze Increase",FUND_FREEZECHANCEINCREASE_DESC:"Bonus Freeze Chance percentage.",FUND_REMEDYINCREASE_LABEL:"Remedy Increase",FUND_REMEDYINCREASE_DESC:"Bonus Remedy percentage.",FUND_HINDERCHANCEINCREASE_LABEL:"Hinder Increase",FUND_HINDERCHANCEINCREASE_DESC:"Bonus Hinder Chance percentage.",FUND_HYPNOTIZECHANCEINCREASE_LABEL:"Hypnotize Increase",FUND_HYPNOTIZECHANCEINCREASE_DESC:"Bonus Hypnotize Chance percentage.",FUND_SLOWCHANCEINCREASE_LABEL:"Slow Increase",FUND_SLOWCHANCEINCREASE_DESC:"Bonus Slow Chance percentage.",FUND_FRAILTYCHANCEINCREASE_LABEL:"Frailty Increase",FUND_FRAILTYCHANCEINCREASE_DESC:"Bonus Frailty Chance percentage.",FUND_HASTECHANCEINCREASE_LABEL:"Haste Increase",FUND_HASTECHANCEINCREASE_DESC:"Bonus Haste Chance percentage.",FUND_ENERGYWAVECHANCEINCREASE_LABEL:"Energy Wave Increase",FUND_ENERGYWAVECHANCEINCREASE_DESC:"Bonus Energy Wave Chance percentage.",FUND_ATTACKDELAY_LABEL:"Attack Speed Bonus",FUND_ATTACKDELAY_DESC:"Attack delay reduction.",FUND_SPEEDCAP_LABEL:"Speed Cap",FUND_SPEEDCAP_DESC:"Minimum attack delay (ms).",FUND_QUINTESSENCEGAIN_LABEL:"Quintessence Gain",FUND_QUINTESSENCEGAIN_DESC:"Bonus Quintessence production for Graphite Concept in Conceptual Synthesizer.",FUND_QUINTESSENCEPINNACLE_LABEL:"Quintessence Pinnacle",FUND_QUINTESSENCEPINNACLE_DESC:`Multiplies Pending Quintessence gain based on the number of sketches that have reached their Maximum Victories during the current Redraw cycle. Boosting your Max Victories limit also provides an exponential increase to this effect.

Formula: (1 + (Max Victories / 10000)) ^ (# of Maxed Sketches)`,FUND_GRAPHITEUPGRADECOST_LABEL:"Graphite Cost",FUND_GRAPHITEUPGRADECOST_DESC:"Graphite cost reduction. Applies to both Tools and Stat Upgrades.",FUND_WAXUPGRADECOST_LABEL:"Wax Cost",FUND_WAXUPGRADECOST_DESC:"Wax cost reduction. Applies to both Tools and Stat Upgrades.",FUND_CHARCOALUPGRADECOST_LABEL:"Charcoal Cost",FUND_CHARCOALUPGRADECOST_DESC:"Charcoal cost reduction. Applies to both Tools and Stat Upgrades.",FUND_COFFEEUPGRADECOST_LABEL:"Coffee Cost",FUND_COFFEEUPGRADECOST_DESC:"Coffee cost reduction. Applies to both Tools and Stat Upgrades.",FUND_INKUPGRADECOST_LABEL:"Ink Cost",FUND_INKUPGRADECOST_DESC:"Ink cost reduction. Applies to both Tools and Stat Upgrades.",FUND_MARKERUPGRADECOST_LABEL:"Marker Cost",FUND_MARKERUPGRADECOST_DESC:"Marker cost reduction. Applies to both Tools and Stat Upgrades.",FUND_ACRYLICUPGRADECOST_LABEL:"Acrylic Cost",FUND_ACRYLICUPGRADECOST_DESC:"Acrylic cost reduction. Applies to both Tools and Stat Upgrades.",FUND_SPRAYUPGRADECOST_LABEL:"Spray Cost",FUND_SPRAYUPGRADECOST_DESC:"Spray cost reduction. Applies to both Tools and Stat Upgrades.",FUND_PHOTONUPGRADECOST_LABEL:"Photon Cost",FUND_PHOTONUPGRADECOST_DESC:"Photon cost reduction. Applies to both Tools and Stat Upgrades.",FUND_GOLDLEAFUPGRADECOST_LABEL:"Gold Leaf Cost",FUND_GOLDLEAFUPGRADECOST_DESC:"Gold Leaf cost reduction. Applies to both Tools and Stat Upgrades.",FUND_GRAPHITEREWARDMULTIPLIER_LABEL:"Graphite Reward",FUND_GRAPHITEREWARDMULTIPLIER_DESC:"Graphite reward multiplier from defeating sketches.",FUND_WAXREWARDMULTIPLIER_LABEL:"Wax Reward",FUND_WAXREWARDMULTIPLIER_DESC:"Wax reward multiplier from defeating sketches.",FUND_CHARCOALREWARDMULTIPLIER_LABEL:"Charcoal Reward",FUND_CHARCOALREWARDMULTIPLIER_DESC:"Charcoal reward multiplier from defeating sketches.",FUND_COFFEEREWARDMULTIPLIER_LABEL:"Coffee Reward",FUND_COFFEEREWARDMULTIPLIER_DESC:"Coffee reward multiplier from defeating sketches.",FUND_INKREWARDMULTIP